lyrics:
[verse]
Walking through the shadows, he's called by his fate
John Wick, the legend, the deadliest to date
Beneath the moonlit sky, vengeance in his eyes
A man of few words, but he'll make you realize

[chorus]
John Wick, a lone wolf in the night
A master assassin, his vengeance ignites
He'll fight till the end, through darkness and despair
No one can stop him, he's beyond compare
style: a "Turkish Rap" in the "Gucci Gang" style
